HEADWORD: Insurancer
<hw>In*sur"an*cer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who effects
insurance; an insurer; an underwriter.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>hose bold <qex>insurancers</qex> of deathless fame.</q>
<rj><qau>Blair.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insurant</ent>⟦br⟧
